command sessionInfo().

Also, it would be important to know from where you got your R version.
If it is from the official Ubuntu repositories, you should file a bug
in the Ubuntu bug tracking system. If it is from CRAN, please revert
here with more information. In any case. as Michael pointed out, it is
necessary to provide more detail on what you did when the problem
appeared and what exactly happened.

Kind regards,

Johannes

