No, we cannot as you didn't even tell us which version os Ubuntu you used.

This works for _a lot_ of people. It also works in countless unattended
installs (as eg on Debian, Launchpad, Travis, ... to build or test packages)
so "something" is different at your end. But from the information supplied we
cannot possibly tell what it may be.

Sorry, Dirk

